-- U.S. bankruptcy judge OKs $120 mln loan for Detroit-reports
-- By Karen Pierog
-- Wed Apr 02, 2014 10:09AM EDT
-- None



April 2 (Reuters) - A U.S. bankruptcy judge on Wednesday approved Detroit's plan to borrow $120 million from Barclays PLC <BARC.L> to improve services in the cash-strapped city, according to newspaper reports.

